<F P=102>  SK0401045994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0405 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0401045994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, January 4 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il-song 
of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea received messages 
of greetings from Borhanoddin Rabbani, president of the Islamic 
State of Afghanistan; Maaouiya Ould Sid 'Ahmed Taya, president 
of the Islamic Republic of Mauritania; Adunyadet Phumiphon, king 
of Thailand; Miguel Trovoada, president of the Democratic 
