secretary general of the Central Committee of the Communist 
Party of Venezuela; Argelia Raya, president of the Movement to 
Socialism of Venezuela; and Betty Frydensbjerg Carlsson, 
chairman of the Communist Party of Denmark. 
  A message came to President Kim Il-song from the Central 
Committee of the October 8 Revolutionary Movement of Brazil. 

