<DOCNO> FBIS3-46722 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas002__a94002" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-002-A </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  4 January 1994 </DATE1>

